= Unload Firewall =
The following script unloads / removes each and every iptables / ip6tables / nftables rule.

{{CodeSelect|code=
sudo nft flush ruleset
}}

= Reload Firewall =
To reload the firewall.

{{CodeSelect|code=
sudo whonix_firewall
}}

